@startuml sequence-license-renewal
title License Renewal - Sequence Diagram

actor "Licensing Employee" as Employee
boundary "DVLD UI" as UI
control "License Service" as LicenseService
control "Test Service" as TestService
database "SQL Server Database" as DB

Employee -> UI : Submit renewal request
UI -> LicenseService : Send license number
LicenseService -> DB : Retrieve license information
DB --> LicenseService : License data

LicenseService -> TestService : Verify vision test
TestService -> DB : Check latest vision test result
DB --> TestService : Vision test status

alt Vision test passed
  LicenseService -> DB : Renew license
  DB --> LicenseService : Renewal saved
  LicenseService --> UI : Display renewed license
else Vision test not passed
  LicenseService --> UI : Request vision test before renewal
end

@enduml